Entries.RequestBody:
{
  "properties": {
    "policy": {
      "enabled": false,
      "rules": [
        {
          "enabled": false,
          "name": "test1",
          "destination": "containerpstestrg8999",
          "definition": {
            "filters": {
              "prefixMatch": [
                "abc",
                "edf",
                "eqwewqe",
                "eqwewqreewqe",
                "qwewqewqewqewqewadasd"
              ],
              "blobTypes": [
                "blockBlob",
                "appendBlob"
              ],
              "includeBlobVersions": true,
              "includeSnapshots": true
            },
            "format": "Parquet",
            "schedule": "Weekly",
            "objectType": "Blob",
            "schemaFields": [
              "Name",
              "Creation-Time",
              "Last-Modified",
              "Content-Length",
              "Content-MD5",
              "BlobType",
              "AccessTier",
              "AccessTierChangeTime",
              "Metadata",
              "AccessTierInferred",
              "Tags",
              "Snapshot",
              "VersionId",
              "IsCurrentVersion"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "enabled": false,
          "name": "test2",
          "destination": "containerpstestrg8999",
          "definition": {
            "filters": {
              "prefixMatch": [
                "con1",
                "con2"
              ]
            },
            "format": "Csv",
            "schedule": "Daily",
            "objectType": "Container",
            "schemaFields": [
              "Name",
              "Metadata",
              "PublicAccess",
              "Last-Modified",
              "LeaseStatus",
              "LeaseState",
              "LeaseDuration",
              "HasImmutabilityPolicy",
              "HasLegalHold",
              "Etag",
              "DefaultEncryptionScope",
              "DenyEncryptionScopeOverride"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "enabled": true,
          "name": "test3",
          "destination": "containerpstestrg8999",
          "definition": {
            "filters": {
              "prefixMatch": [
                "abc1",
                "edf1"
              ],
              "excludePrefix": [
                "aaa1",
                "bbb1"
              ],
              "blobTypes": [
                "appendBlob"
              ],
              "includeDeleted": true
            },
            "format": "Csv",
            "schedule": "Weekly",
            "objectType": "Blob",
            "schemaFields": [
              "Name",
              "Deleted",
              "RemainingRetentionDays",
              "Content-Type",
              "Content-Language",
              "Cache-Control",
              "Content-Disposition"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "type": "Inventory"
    }
  }
}
